articles.title: Covid cases may have peaked for this year, data suggest - Telegraph.co.uk
articles.description: As cases soar in Europe, King's College London finds number with symptomatic virus in Britain is down 4.7 per cent from last week
articles.content:
Covid cases in the UK have peaked for 2021, real-world data from King's College London (KCL) suggests.
